, making it ideal for occasionaluses.andM;ATandamp;T`s version of international virtual network service, ATandamp;T Global SoftwareDefined Network services allow businesses to design their own private dialingplan for calls within the network.andP;  It features fast call-set-up times,high-quality transmission and greater management over internalcommunications.andM;Key Executive: Elaine Kaup, Deputy Director -- ATandamp;T International DedicatedServices.andO;</TEXT></DOC>